data.description: A cozy welcoming home in Silver Springs, Nevada! Surrounded by stunning mountain views, this charming single-story, single-family home has been thoughtfully updated, offering a beautifully modern interior that perfectly complements its natural surroundings. With 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom spanning 1080 sq ft, this home provides both comfort and style on a generous 4.77-acre lot. Welcoming you inside is a delightful kitchen with a built-in dishwasher, built-in microwave, pantry, gas cooktop, built-in single oven, and a removable island. The white cabinetry, granite countertops, and tile backsplash create an elegant ambiance that's both functional and inviting. The adjoining living room features large windows that fill the space with natural light. A ceiling fan complements the wood-look laminate flooring, making this room perfect for unwinding at the end of the day. The bathroom offers modern paint hues, built-in shelving and a shower/tub combo. Not included in the square footage is an enclosed patio space, currently in use as a private home gym. For the tech-savvy homeowner, programmable lights offer personalized ambience, while the well pump compressor, replaced in 2022, guarantees worry-free water supply. The convenience of a private well and septic system ensures a self-sufficient lifestyle, while the owned propane tank and low-maintenance exterior enhance the ease of living. The exterior space is a blank canvas waiting for the next owner to make it their own. This property possesses a detached oversized 2-car garage and plenty of space for RV parking and outdoor toys. With ample room to explore, your vision of the perfect outdoor space can come to life. Just a short drive leads you to the Carson River, Lahontan Reservoir, Highway 95 and US 50. This charming home is an opportunity not to be missed. The entire exterior has brand new paint even on the garage and shed as well. Embrace modern comforts and create the property you’ve always envisioned – schedule your showing today
